            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a<strong> </strong>drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> pepper strips</strong> and<strong> sliced shallot </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your<strong> black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1717777699843-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1717777699843-x400.jpg",
